--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.4.2 (2020-11-08)
E: Add reload capability to systemd service unit file

* Version 0.4.1 (2020-10-30)
E: Simplify Ansible file header (ansible_managed)

* Version 0.4.0 (2020-10-08)
C: Reset default-rule-path to '/var/lib/suricata/rules'
F: Add option to manage custom rules (suricata_config)
F: Alter suricata-update command to load custom rules

* Version 0.3.1 (2020-09-24)
E: Change Suricata user-agent

* Version 0.3.0 (2020-09-22)
F: Add option to define EXTERNAL_NET (suricata_external_net)
F: Add option to define HOME_NET (suricata_home_net)

* Version 0.2.0 (2020-09-22)
F: Add systemd service unit file to manage promiscuous mode

* Version 0.1.0 (2020-09-22)
F: Initial release
